originalSql:
SELECT 
    CONCAT('Supplier: ', s.s_name, ' (', s.s_suppkey, ')') AS supplier_info,
    COUNT(DISTINCT ps.ps_partkey) AS total_parts_supplied,
    SUM(ps.ps_availqty) AS total_available_quantity,
    AVG(ps.ps_supplycost) AS average_supply_cost,
    STRING_AGG(DISTINCT CONCAT('Part: ', p.p_name, ' [', p.p_partkey, '] - Price: $', p.p_retailprice), ', ') AS parts_details,
    r.r_name AS region_name
FROM 
    supplier s
JOIN 
    partsupp ps ON s.s_suppkey = ps.ps_suppkey
JOIN 
    part p ON ps.ps_partkey = p.p_partkey
JOIN 
    nation n ON s.s_nationkey = n.n_nationkey
JOIN 
    region r ON n.n_regionkey = r.r_regionkey
WHERE 
    r.r_name LIKE '%East%' 
GROUP BY 
    s.s_suppkey, s.s_name, r.r_name
HAVING 
    COUNT(DISTINCT ps.ps_partkey) > 5
ORDER BY 
    total_available_quantity DESC

FROM "partsupp"

SELECT COALESCE("t4"."SUPPLIER_INFO", "t4"."SUPPLIER_INFO") AS "SUPPLIER_INFO", "t4"."TOTAL_PARTS_SUPPLIED", "t4"."TOTAL_AVAILABLE_QUANTITY", "t4"."AVERAGE_SUPPLY_COST", "t4"."PARTS_DETAILS", "t4"."REGION_NAME"
FROM (SELECT "supplier"."s_suppkey", "supplier"."s_name", "t0"."r_name", MIN(CONCAT('Supplier: ', "supplier"."s_name", ' (', CAST("supplier"."s_suppkey" AS VARCHAR), ')')) AS "SUPPLIER_INFO", COUNT(DISTINCT "s1"."ps_partkey") AS "TOTAL_PARTS_SUPPLIED", SUM("s1"."ps_availqty") AS "TOTAL_AVAILABLE_QUANTITY", AVG("s1"."ps_supplycost") AS "AVERAGE_SUPPLY_COST", LISTAGG(DISTINCT CONCAT('Part: ', "part"."p_name", ' [', CAST("part"."p_partkey" AS VARCHAR), '] - Price: $', CAST("part"."p_retailprice" AS VARCHAR)), ', ') AS "PARTS_DETAILS", MIN("t0"."r_name") AS "REGION_NAME"
FROM (SELECT *
FROM "region"
WHERE "r_name" LIKE '%East%') AS "t0"
INNER JOIN "nation" ON "t0"."r_regionkey" = "nation"."n_regionkey"
INNER JOIN "supplier" ON "nation"."n_nationkey" = "supplier"."s_nationkey"
INNER JOIN ("part" INNER JOIN "s1" ON "part"."p_partkey" = "s1"."ps_partkey") ON "supplier"."s_suppkey" = "s1"."ps_suppkey"
GROUP BY "supplier"."s_suppkey", "supplier"."s_name", "t0"."r_name"
HAVING COUNT(DISTINCT "s1"."ps_partkey") > 5
ORDER BY 6 DESC NULLS FIRST) AS "t4"
